{"word":"G1967 - ἐπιούσιος - epioúsios - ep-ee-oo'-see-os - Daily","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιούσιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epioúsios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-oo'-see-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Daily</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தேவை, தேவையான அப்பம், அன்றன்று - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"the bread of our necessity, necessary for us, daily"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Perhaps from the same as <a href=\"#/G1966 - ἐπιοῦσα - epioûsa - ep-ee-oo'-sah/1966\">G1966</a>; <i>to-morrow's</i>; but more probably from <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and a derivative of the present participle feminine of <a href=\"#/G1510 - εἰμί - eimí - i-mee'/1510\">G1510</a>; <i>for subsistence</i>, that is, <i>needful:</i> - daily.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}